    {
      "id": 246500,
      "postNumber": 6,
      "createdAt": "2026-02-25T07:11:07.344Z",
      "author": "DavidSchenkler (David Schenkler | monday ambassador cohort 7)",
      "cookedHtml": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n<img alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://avatars.discourse-cdn.com/v4/letter/z/eb8c5e/48.png\" class=\"avatar\" /> zohreh:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>ich möchte 2 spalte stunde minus machen in monday und ergebnius in zahlen splate spiechern , wie kann ich?</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>Hi <a class=\"mention\" href=\"/u/zohreh\">@zohreh</a> ,</p>\n<p>Since you have the Enterprise plan, I suggest using <a class=\"hashtag-cooked\" href=\"/tag/workflows/487\"><span class=\"hashtag-icon-placeholder\"></span><span>workflows</span></a> (Workflow Builder). Also, download the app <strong>Workflow Blocks: Formula</strong> by SpicyTab. It’s Free to use. Follow the steps below and it should work like a charm.</p>\n<p>Your <strong>Trigger</strong> will be “When Art Personal changes”.</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/0/5/053c0395b1be1fceaf1e21e24808589c6341f3ed.png\" title=\"Screenshot 2026-02-25 at 11.07.10\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/0/5/053c0395b1be1fceaf1e21e24808589c6341f3ed_2_197x500.png\" alt=\"Screenshot 2026-02-25 at 11.07.10\" width=\"197\" height=\"500\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Screenshot 2026-02-25 at 11.07.10</span><span class=\"informations\">297×751 36.8 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/e/a/ea54cef8cb65e3d4888c8ecc0b14e2f314615a8f.png\" title=\"Screenshot 2026-02-25 at 11.08.07\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/e/a/ea54cef8cb65e3d4888c8ecc0b14e2f314615a8f_2_690x340.png\" alt=\"Screenshot 2026-02-25 at 11.08.07\" width=\"690\" height=\"340\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"fi